From de0434dc07f287385726078f5749101a4532152b Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Claude <claude@anthropic.com>
Date: Thu, 9 Jul 2026 20:28:48 +0000
Subject: [PATCH] App mobile offline-first: build local + SQLite/IndexedDB sync
 + Capgo live update + fix CI + rotation keystore

---
